    • Stable Data Transmission: Wired Type-C connection provides the gaming keyboard more stable transmission. Separation of bond wires, humanized designmore convenient.
    • Ergonomic Design and Mechanical Feel: For this membrane keyboard, the size of Enter key, height of the keycap, honest style and other ergonomic designs make people relaxed and enjoy excellent mechanical feel.
    • Elegant Appearance: Pure white and mature pink, complementary to each other, set off in 6 backlight effects and 8 backlight color.In addition, the characters are transparent and luminous.The cute keyboard is more beautiful and makes people happy and relieve stress.

    Product Description

    Description of Some Noteworthy Questions

    • What continuous improvement of product quality has been done

    Milky white middle frame is replaced with a transparent middle frame, and the true RGB is more brighter.The ESC key is moved from the side to the top for direct use, which is more convenient.Key cap upgraded to double - color injection molding, character transparent luminous.

    • How to use the arrow keys of this mini keyboard?

    Fn+W switch WSAD and up,down,left and right direction keys.Switch back and forth as needed.WASD is the scientific position of the arrow keys that is the consensus of the gaming industry.

    • Why is there no foot when designing the Snpurdiri 60 keyboard scheme?

    Guided by loyalty to customer needs, after research, most European and American gaming keyboard users like the honest style.

    • Can it work on game consoles such as PS4/Xbox etc?

    You can play PS4 through Snpurdiri 60 percent gaming keyboard.But you need choose gaming keyboard adapter that can support the corresponding game console. The converter from the same company SnpurTech, another brand DGG adapter is tested and supports Switch/Xbox one/Xbox 360/PS 4/PS 3/Xbox Series S/Xbox Series X.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Mister Tango
    4.0 out of 5 stars For the price, you can't bear it.
    Reviewed in the United States on May 5, 2023
    Color: BlackVerified Purchase
    For the price, this keyboard an easy purchase that doesn't feel intimidating like many mechanical keyboards can. It's a 60%, which I've found is a little awkward since it's missing the traditional (4) arrow keys. BUT it does provide them through using modified keys. The arrows are printed along the fronts of for letter keys. It's a nice workaround, but may need some custom key reassignments. But I was honestly surprised by the thoughtful inclusion. I happened to buy a 75% keyboard in the same order, and I will say I prefer that since it has the dedicated arrow keys while barely making the footprint larger.

    This keyboard is compact and quiet. No big clicks. And it's illuminated, which is a huge plus in my workspace. It's hard wired with a USB cord coming out the back. The 75% I bought has a detachable USB C cable, and I find that to be more convenient since you can swap out another keyboard without messing with the other end of the cable. But regardless, it still works just fine.

    The bottom line for me is that this is not a bad keyboard for around $20. It's actually one of the rare purchases that felt like what I received was way better than I would normally be expecting for the price.

And both of the keyboards were made out of plastic, the case doesn't have stands, and the keyboard itself sits pretty high up for a 60% keyboard. But on the other hand, I would say the RGB looks fantastic. I would not repurchase it, but the price is the best buy for a keyboard, I would say.
